20:38.171 --> 20:39.481
How was I supposed to know
you were gonna be here?

20:39.642 --> 20:40.836
Yeah, well, this is where I live.

20:41.068 --> 20:43.045
- So you better...
- Explains the longhorn on the wall.

20:43.849 --> 20:45.843
- (Snickers)
- You think this is funny?

20:46.040 --> 20:49.767
No. I think it's incredibly sad.

20:52.393 --> 20:53.615
<i>♪ Where all the honey goes</i>

20:53.876 --> 20:56.507
<i>♪ But you hope it and
you pray real hard ♪</i>

